Put commands which need to be executed at the command line, or by application
programs here.  This directory will automaticaly be included the path for all
running services.

Some files you may find here:

chaplocal
  This is a template for the chaplocal program, used to set up a container
  development environment.

get-chaplocal
  Executed as a --task to retrieve a custom version of the 'chaplocal' script.

get-help
  Executed as a --task to provide help for the image (see ../etc/task-templates)

get-launcher
  Executed as a --task to create launch scripts to launch the image
  (see ../etc/task-templates)
